  <body>
		<span><h2>Healthcoin - Node Information Server</h2></span>
		
		<div>
			<span><h4>Usage:</h4></span>

			<span><h4>Standard Healthcoin RPC Commands:</h4></span>
			<span>/help -- returns Healthcoin RPC commands (most are implemented)</span><br />

			<span><h4>Custom Healthcoin Commands:</h4></span>
			<span>/totalhealthcoin -- returns total number of Healthcoin in existence</span><br />
			<span>/blockcount -- returns current block height</span><br />
			<span>/difficulty -- returns current PoW and PoS difficulty</span><br />
			<span>/gettx/<%= "<txid>" %> -- returns information about this transaction</span><br />
			<span>/getblockhash/<%= "<index>" %> -- returns the requested block hash</span><br />
			<span>/getblock/<%= "<hash>" %> -- returns information about this block</span><br />
			<span>/getpeers -- returns list of currently connected peers</span><br />
			
		</div>
  </body>
